如果你无法找到FlushRenderingCommandsInternal()方法，可能是因为UE4的代码库中有一些不同版本的代码库，其中某些版本可能对这个方法进行了修改或移除。不过，一般来说，FlushRenderingCommands()的具体实现仍然在RenderingThread.cpp文件中，你可以在该文件中查找到类似下面这样的代码：

```
void FRenderingThread::FlushRenderingCommands()
{
    ...
    Fence.Wait();
    ...
}

void FRenderingThread::FlushRenderingCommandsInternal()
{
    ...
}
```

FlushRenderingCommands()会调用FlushRenderingCommandsInternal()方法，而FlushRenderingCommandsInternal()包含了Fence.Wait()结束等待的代码。你可以在RenderingThread.cpp文件中根据这些关键词进行搜索。

class RENDERCORE_API FRenderCommandFence
{
public:

	/**
	 * Adds a fence command to the rendering command queue.
	 * Conceptually, the pending fence count is incremented to reflect the pending fence command.
	 * Once the rendering thread has executed the fence command, it decrements the pending fence count.
	 * @param bSyncToRHIAndGPU, true if we should wait for the RHI thread or GPU, otherwise we only wait for the render thread.
	 */
	void BeginFence(bool bSyncToRHIAndGPU = false);

	/**
	 * Waits for pending fence commands to retire.
	 * @param bProcessGameThreadTasks, if true we are on a short callstack where it is safe to process arbitrary game thread tasks while we wait
	 */
	void Wait(bool bProcessGameThreadTasks = false) const;

	// return true if the fence is complete
	bool IsFenceComplete() const;

private:
	/** Graph event that represents completion of this fence **/
	mutable FGraphEventRef CompletionEvent;
	/** Thread that will trigger the CompletionEvent **/
	ENamedThreads::Type TriggerThreadIndex;
};

在RHIThread::Run()方法中，有一个主循环，其中调用了ProcessTasksUntilQuit()方法，用于不断获取和处理异步任务直到线程退出。具体代码实现如下（摘自Engine\Source\Runtime\RenderCore\Private\RenderingThread.cpp文件）：

```
void RHIThread::Run()
{
    ...
    while (!bQuitThread)
    {
        FPlatformProcess::Sleep(0.0f);
        FPlatformMisc::HandleSystemError();

        // Process async tasks until there are none left
        ProcessAsyncTasks(GetMaxMillisecondsForAsyncTaskProcessing());

        // Clear the requested quit flag if there are no outstanding tasks
        if (AreAsyncTasksComplete())
        {
            RequestQuit();
        }
    }

    // Process tasks until there are no more
    ProcessTasksUntilQuit();
}
```

在这段代码中，ProcessAsyncTasks()方法在每次循环迭代中被调用，用于异步获取和处理渲染命令。同时，AreAsyncTasksComplete()方法用于检查是否还有待处理的异步任务。如果没有，则使用RequestQuit()方法请求退出渲染线程。

在退出处理循环之后，RHIThread::Run()方法会继续调用ProcessTasksUntilQuit()方法，用于处理所有未完成的任务，以确保所有命令都得到了执行。通过这样的方式，RHIThread::Run()方法确保了渲染线程能够在所有渲染任务都得到处理后正常退出。
